all trading suspended.

690
00:44:46,000 --> 00:44:48,879
But... but... I've got a...

691
00:44:48,880 --> 00:44:50,799
I've got a bankers draft!

692
00:44:50,800 --> 00:44:54,319
Here! Look!
It's a bank draft!

693
00:44:54,320 --> 00:44:56,479
See! They have to pay it!

694
00:44:56,480 --> 00:44:59,560
Like I said, I'm sorry, sir, but
all trading has been suspended.

695
00:45:07,240 --> 00:45:11,199
- Bankers draft or direct transfers.
- Agreed.

696
00:45:11,200 --> 00:45:13,680
Looks like you've found
your uk supplier.

697
00:45:15,640 --> 00:45:18,778
Good. This friend of mine got
two tickets for the archery,

698
00:45:18,779 --> 00:45:20,679
